{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Rev|18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","chapter":18,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":1,"text":"After this I saw another angel with great authority coming down from heaven, and the earth was illuminated by his splendor.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":2,"text":"He called out in a mighty voice:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":3,"text":"For all the nations have drunk","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":4,"text":"Then I heard another voice from heaven:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":5,"text":"For her sins are piled up to heaven,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":6,"text":"Pay her back the way she also paid,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":7,"text":"As much as she glorified herself and indulged her sensual and excessive ways,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":8,"text":"For this reason her plagues will come in just one day —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":9,"text":"The kings of the earth who have committed sexual immorality and shared her sensual and excessive ways will weep and mourn over her when they see the smoke from her burning.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":10,"text":"They will stand far off in fear of her torment, saying,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":11,"text":"The merchants of the earth will weep and mourn over her, because no one buys their cargo any longer —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":12,"text":"cargo of gold, silver, jewels, and pearls; fine linen, purple, silk, and scarlet; all kinds of fragrant wood products; objects of ivory; objects of expensive wood, brass, iron, and marble;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":13,"text":"cinnamon, spice, incense, myrrh, and frankincense; wine, olive oil, fine flour, and grain; cattle and sheep; horses and carriages; and slaves —human lives.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":14,"text":"The fruit you craved has left you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":15,"text":"The merchants of these things, who became rich from her, will stand far off in fear of her torment, weeping and mourning,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":16,"text":"saying,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":17,"text":"for in a single hour","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":18,"text":"as they watched the smoke from her burning and kept crying out, “Who was like the great city?”","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":19,"text":"They threw dust on their heads and kept crying out, weeping, and mourning,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":20,"text":"Rejoice over her, heaven,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":21,"text":"Then a mighty angel picked up a stone like a large millstone and threw it into the sea, saying,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":22,"text":"The sound of harpists, musicians,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":23,"text":"the light of a lamp","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rev:18:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rev","bookOrder":65,"chapter":18,"verse":24,"text"